HEADWORD: Seminoles
<hw>Sem"i*noles</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>; <sing>sing.
<singw>Seminole</singw> <pr>(<?/)</pr></sing>. <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld>
